<body>
<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1063259" n="1"/>   
<opener><salute>Viro Nobilissimo, Clarissimo Doctissimo<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice>
    <lb/>Domino <rs type="person">Nicolao Bernoulli</rs>, Professo<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ri Philosophi<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> in <rs type="organisation">Academia Basi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>leensi</rs> <choice><orig><g ref="#etlig">&amp;</g></orig><reg>et</reg></choice> <rs type="organisation">Regi<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> Societatis Berolinen<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>sis</rs> Sodali.
    <lb/><abbr>S. P. D.</abbr>
    <lb/><rs type="person">Lud. Cöper</rs></salute></opener>
  <p><lb/>Cum non ita pridem <date>28. scilicet Apri<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>lis</date> <rs type="person">Theodorus Jablonsk<choice><orig><g ref="#ydots">ÿ</g></orig><reg>y</reg></choice></rs>, Secretarius olim
    <lb/><rs type="organisation">Societatis Regi<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> scientiarum</rs>, <date>diem</date> obie<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>rit supremum, jussa <rs type="organisation">Societatis</rs> et pro<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>prio motu partium mearum esse du<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>xi, ea de re Te, Vir Clarissime, certio<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
  <pb facs="1063260" n="2"/>
    <lb break="no"/>rem facere. Fuit Defunctus Ornamen<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tum rei literari<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>, iis<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> virtutibus or<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>natus, ut in paucis inclaruerit, omni<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>bus<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> bonis,<!-- ToDo: Kontrollieren, ob das wirklich ein Komma ist. --> gratus at<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> admirationi ex<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>isteret. Labore et industria nemini ces<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>sit, variis<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> artis et natur<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> donis mul<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tis signum pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>tulit. Nullus dubito, quin
    <lb/>Tu, Vir Clarissime, propter commune <rs type="organisation">So<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>cietatis</rs> vinculum tristissimo hoc luctu
    <lb/>commovearis, eum <rs type="person">Collegam</rs> non modo
    <lb/>facillimum et Fidissimum studiorum
    <lb/>asseclam amiserimus, cujus consili<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>um et matura prudentia quovis
    <lb/>tempore subsidio nobis fuit, studio<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>rum<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> suavitas et venustas omnium<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> 
  <pb facs="1063261" n="3"/> 
    <lb/><lb/>seculorum consummata cognitio, varia<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>rum linguarum nitor et elegantia non
    <lb/>minorem voluptatem adferebant. Id<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>circo omnes, qui studiis virtuti<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice>
    <lb/>aliquem honorem tribuunt, Eum perpe<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tuo moerebunt, nullo non tempore
    <lb/>operam daturi, ut ejus exemplo exci<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tati ad parem laudem virtutis et glo<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ri<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> perveniant. Ad me quod attinet,
    <lb/>cui ejus partes certa ratione ante
    <lb/>aliquot annos jam demandat<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> fue<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>runt, Te, Vir Clarissime, ea, qua par
    <lb/>est, observantia rogo at<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> obtestor,
    <lb/>ut me in beate Defuncti locum
    <lb/>ac amicitiam admittas, persuasum<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> 
  <pb facs="1063262" n="4"/> 
  <lb/>Tibi habeas, me pro viribus vestigia
    <lb/>illius secuturum, Te semper in oculis
    <lb/>habiturum, at<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> ad omnia humanitatis
    <lb/>officia, literarum<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> commercia para<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tissimum fore. Pergratum erit <rs type="organisation">Socie<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tati</rs> nostr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>, cum Tibi, Vir Clarissime,
    <lb/>placuerit, ad ejus decus et incremen<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tum studia Tua conferre, at<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> commu<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>nicatione rerum earum, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> ad rem li<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>terariam pertinent, cum primis vero ad
    <lb/>Philosophiam spectant, auxilio esse, pro
    <lb/>quo Tuo officio eadem nullo non tem<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>pore debitam gratiam habebit. </p><closer>Vale, Vir
      <lb/>Clarissime, me<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> addictissimis Tuis
      <lb/>annumerare non dedignare. <dateline><rs type="place">Berolini</rs>
        <lb/>die <date when="1731-06-07">7. Junii 1731</date>.</dateline></closer>
</div>
